            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 luq-gradient-text">üéØ Why Plugin Categories Matter</h2>
            <p class="text-luq-neutral-700 dark:text-luq-neutral-300 mb-6">
              Plugin categories aren't just organizational tools‚Äîthey're <strong>essential for controlling type variables in ChainableFieldBuilder</strong>. Each category determines what type parameters are passed to the builder, ensuring complete type safety.
            </p>
            
